  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "for the time being, we only received this request once four years ago, so didn't look into how it would work to merge the parameters. I think for advanced use cases like you're describing, it will be best to reference what we do ourselves in the eg. refinement list connector and edit that for your use case, rather than using configure.",
